## Non-negotiables

<!-- Universal procedural rules that apply to every change. State each rule
     once, abstractly. Triggers and path-scoped actions belong in Boundaries. -->

- Use plan mode when any Ask-first condition triggers (see Boundaries).
- No placeholder comments. Ask if you lack context.
- Use `<pkg-mgr>` only; do not introduce alternatives.
- Run the fast verification after every meaningful change.

